  <summary date="2019-06-18T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Locking Up Robocallers Act of 2019

This bill requires the Federal Communications Commission, upon obtaining evidence that suggests an intentional robocall violation, to provide such evidence to the Department of Justice and to report annually on the number and type of such instances.</summary>
